#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "CDI Integration Guide"
msgstr "Guia de IntegraĂ§ĂŁo do CDI"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"ArC, the CDI container in Quarkus, is bootstrapped at build time.\n"
"To integrate with the container, https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1.html#spi_lite[CDI Build Compatible Extensions, window=\"_blank\"] can be used, as well as a Quarkus-specific extension API.\n"
"CDI Portable Extensions are not and cannot be supported.\n"
"This guide focuses on the Quarkus-specific extensions API."
msgstr "O ArC, o contĂŞiner CDI no Quarkus, ĂŠ inicializado durante a compilaĂ§ĂŁo. Para integrar-se ao contĂŞiner, podem ser utilizadas link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1.html#spi_lite[as ExtensĂľes CompatĂ­veis com CompilaĂ§ĂŁo do CDI] , bem como uma API de extensĂľes especĂ­fica do Quarkus. As ExtensĂľes PortĂĄteis do CDI nĂŁo sĂŁo e nĂŁo podem ser suportadas. Este guia concentra-se na API de extensĂľes especĂ­fica do Quarkus."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The container is bootstrapped in multiple phases.\n"
"From a high level perspective these phases go as follows:"
msgstr "O contĂŞiner ĂŠ inicializado em vĂĄrias fases. De uma perspectiva geral, essas fases sĂŁo as seguintes:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Initialization"
msgstr "InicializaĂ§ĂŁo"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Bean discovery"
msgstr "Descoberta do feijĂŁo"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Registration of synthetic components"
msgstr "Registro de componentes sintĂŠticos"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Validation"
msgstr "ValidaĂ§ĂŁo"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In the _initialization_ phase, the preparatory work is being carried out, and custom contexts are registered.\n"
"_Bean discovery_ is then the process where the container analyzes all application classes, identifies beans and wires them all together based on the provided metadata.\n"
"Subsequently, the extensions can register _synthetic components_.\n"
"Attributes of these components are fully controlled by the extensions, i.e. are not derived from an existing class.\n"
"Finally, the _deployment is validated_.\n"
"For example, the container validates every injection point in the application and fails the build if there is no bean that satisfies the given required type and qualifiers."
msgstr "Na fase _de inicializaĂ§ĂŁo_ , o trabalho preparatĂłrio estĂĄ sendo realizado e os contextos personalizados sĂŁo registrados. _A descoberta de beans_ ĂŠ, entĂŁo, o processo em que o contĂŞiner analisa todas as classes da aplicaĂ§ĂŁo, identifica os beans e os conecta entre si com base nos metadados fornecidos. Posteriormente, as extensĂľes podem registrar _componentes sintĂŠticos_ . Os atributos desses componentes sĂŁo totalmente controlados pelas extensĂľes, ou seja, nĂŁo sĂŁo derivados de uma classe existente. Por fim, a _implantaĂ§ĂŁo ĂŠ validada_ . Por exemplo, o contĂŞiner valida cada ponto de injeĂ§ĂŁo na aplicaĂ§ĂŁo e rejeita a compilaĂ§ĂŁo caso nĂŁo haja nenhum bean que satisfaĂ§a o tipo e os qualificadores exigidos."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can see more information about the bootstrap by enabling additional logging. Simply run the Maven build with `-X` or `--debug` and grep the lines that contain `io.quarkus.arc`. In <<cdi-reference.adoc#dev_mode,dev mode>>, you can use `quarkus.log.category.\"io.quarkus.arc.processor\".level=DEBUG` and two special endpoints are also registered automatically to provide some basic debug info in the JSON format."
msgstr "Ă possĂ­vel obter mais informaĂ§Ăľes sobre o bootstrap ativando o registro de log adicional. Basta executar a compilaĂ§ĂŁo do Maven com `a opĂ§ĂŁo -X` ou `--debug` e localizar as linhas que contĂŞm `io.quarkus.arc` . No xref:cdi-reference.adoc#dev_mode[modo de desenvolvimento] , ĂŠ possĂ­vel utilizar `quarkus.log.category.\"io.quarkus.arc.processor\".level=DEBUG` ; alĂŠm disso, dois endpoints especiais tambĂŠm sĂŁo registrados automaticamente para fornecer algumas informaĂ§Ăľes bĂĄsicas de depuraĂ§ĂŁo no formato JSON."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus build steps can produce and consume various build items and hook into each phase.\n"
"In the following sections, we will describe all the relevant build items and common scenarios."
msgstr "As etapas de compilaĂ§ĂŁo do Quarkus podem produzir e utilizar diversos itens de compilaĂ§ĂŁo, alĂŠm de se integrar a cada fase. Nas seĂ§Ăľes a seguir, descreveremos todos os itens de compilaĂ§ĂŁo relevantes e os cenĂĄrios mais comuns."

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Metadata Sources"
msgstr "Fontes de metadados"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Classes and annotations are the primary source of bean-level metadata.\n"
"The initial metadata are read from the _bean archive index_, an immutable https://github.com/smallrye/jandex[Jandex index, window=\"_blank\"] which is built from various sources during <<cdi-reference.adoc#bean_discovery,bean discovery>>.\n"
"However, extensions can add, remove or transform the metadata at certain stages of the bootstrap.\n"
"Moreover, extensions can also register <<synthetic_beans,synthetic components>>.\n"
"This is an important aspect to realize when integrating CDI components in Quarkus."
msgstr "As classes e as anotaĂ§Ăľes sĂŁo a principal fonte de metadados no nĂ­vel dos beans. Os metadados iniciais sĂŁo lidos a partir do _Ă­ndice do arquivo de beans_ , um link:https://github.com/smallrye/jandex[Ă­ndice Jandex] imutĂĄvel que ĂŠ construĂ­do a partir de vĂĄrias fontes durante xref:cdi-reference.adoc#bean_discovery[a descoberta dos beans] . No entanto, as extensĂľes podem adicionar, remover ou transformar os metadados em determinadas etapas do bootstrap. AlĂŠm disso, as extensĂľes tambĂŠm podem registrar xref:synthetic_beans[componentes sintĂŠticos] . Esse ĂŠ um aspecto importante a ser considerado ao integrar componentes CDI no Quarkus."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This way, extensions can turn classes, that would be otherwise ignored, into beans and vice versa.\n"
"For example, a class that declares a `@Scheduled` method is always registered as a bean even if it is not annotated with a bean defining annotation and would be normally ignored."
msgstr "Dessa forma, as extensĂľes podem transformar classes â que, de outra forma, seriam ignoradas â em beans e vice-versa. Por exemplo, uma classe que declara um mĂŠtodo `@Scheduled` ĂŠ sempre registrada como um bean, mesmo que nĂŁo esteja anotada com uma anotaĂ§ĂŁo que defina um bean e, normalmente, seria ignorada."

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Use Case - My Class Is Not Recognized as a Bean"
msgstr "Caso de uso â Minha classe nĂŁo ĂŠ reconhecida como um bean"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An `UnsatisfiedResolutionException` indicates a problem during <<cdi.adoc#typesafe_resolution,typesafe resolution>>.\n"
"Sometimes an injection point cannot be satisfied even if there is a class on the classpath that appears to be eligible for injection.\n"
"There are several reasons why a class is not recognized and also several ways to fix it.\n"
"In the first step, we should identify the _reason_."
msgstr "Uma exceĂ§ĂŁo ``UnsatisfiedResolutionException`` indica um problema durante xref:cdi.adoc#typesafe_resolution[a resoluĂ§ĂŁo com seguranĂ§a de tipos] . Ăs vezes, um ponto de injeĂ§ĂŁo nĂŁo pode ser atendido, mesmo que haja uma classe no classpath que pareĂ§a ser elegĂ­vel para injeĂ§ĂŁo. Existem vĂĄrias razĂľes pelas quais uma classe nĂŁo ĂŠ reconhecida e tambĂŠm vĂĄrias maneiras de corrigir isso. Na primeira etapa, devemos identificar a _causa_ ."

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_Reason 1_: Class Is Not discovered"
msgstr "_Motivo 1_ : A classe nĂŁo foi encontrada"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus has a <<cdi-reference.adoc#bean_discovery,simplified discovery>>.\n"
"It might happen that the class is not part of the application index.\n"
"For example, classes from the _runtime module_ of a Quarkus extension are not indexed automatically."
msgstr "O Quarkus possui um xref:cdi-reference.adoc#bean_discovery[mecanismo de descoberta simplificado] . Pode ocorrer que a classe nĂŁo faĂ§a parte do Ă­ndice da aplicaĂ§ĂŁo. Por exemplo, as classes do _mĂłdulo de tempo de execuĂ§ĂŁo_ de uma extensĂŁo do Quarkus nĂŁo sĂŁo indexadas automaticamente."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"_Solution_: Use the `AdditionalBeanBuildItem`.\n"
"This build item can be used to specify one or more additional classes to be analyzed during the discovery.\n"
"Additional bean classes are transparently added to the application index processed by the container."
msgstr "_SoluĂ§ĂŁo_ : Utilize o `AdditionalBeanBuildItem` . Esse item de compilaĂ§ĂŁo pode ser usado para especificar uma ou mais classes adicionais a serem analisadas durante a descoberta. As classes de beans adicionais sĂŁo adicionadas de forma transparente ao Ă­ndice da aplicaĂ§ĂŁo processado pelo contĂŞiner."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It is not possible to conditionally enable/disable additional beans via the `@IfBuildProfile`, `@UnlessBuildProfile`, `@IfBuildProperty` and `@UnlessBuildProperty` annotations as described in <<cdi-reference.adoc#enable_build_profile>> and <<cdi-reference.adoc#enable_build_properties>>. Extensions should inspect the configuration or the current profile and only produce an `AdditionalBeanBuildItem` if really needed."
msgstr "NĂŁo ĂŠ possĂ­vel ativar/desativar condicionalmente beans adicionais por meio das anotaĂ§Ăľes `@IfBuildProfile` , `@UnlessBuildProfile` , `@IfBuildProperty` e `@UnlessBuildProperty` , conforme descrito em <<cdi-reference.adoc#enable_build_profile>> e <<cdi-reference.adoc#enable_build_properties>> . As extensĂľes devem verificar a configuraĂ§ĂŁo ou o perfil atual e apenas gerar um `AdditionalBeanBuildItem` se for realmente necessĂĄrio."

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`AdditionalBeanBuildItem` Example"
msgstr "Exemplo de `AdditionalBeanBuildItem`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`AdditionalBeanBuildItem.Builder` can be used for more complex use cases."
msgstr "`O` ` `AdditionalBeanBuildItem.Builder` ` pode ser utilizado para casos de uso mais complexos."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Bean classes added via `AdditionalBeanBuildItem` are _removable_ by default.\n"
"If the container considers them <<cdi-reference.adoc#remove_unused_beans,unused>>, they are just ignored.\n"
"However, you can use `AdditionalBeanBuildItem.Builder.setUnremovable()` method to instruct the container to never remove bean classes registered via this build item.\n"
"See also <<cdi-reference.adoc#remove_unused_beans,Removing Unused Beans>> and <<unremovable_builditem>> for more details."
msgstr "As classes de bean adicionadas por meio `do `AdditionalBeanBuildItem`` sĂŁo _removĂ­veis_ por padrĂŁo. Se o contĂŞiner as considerar xref:cdi-reference.adoc#remove_unused_beans[nĂŁo utilizadas] , elas serĂŁo simplesmente ignoradas. No entanto, ĂŠ possĂ­vel utilizar o mĂŠtodo ``AdditionalBeanBuildItem.Builder.setUnremovable()` ` para instruir o contĂŞiner a nunca remover as classes de bean registradas por meio desse item de construĂ§ĂŁo. Consulte tambĂŠm xref:cdi-reference.adoc#remove_unused_beans[âRemovendo beans nĂŁo utilizados] â e â <<unremovable_builditem>> â para obter mais detalhes."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It is also possible to set the default scope via `AdditionalBeanBuildItem.Builder#setDefaultScope()`.\n"
"The default scope is only used if there is no scope declared on the bean class."
msgstr "TambĂŠm ĂŠ possĂ­vel definir o escopo padrĂŁo por meio do mĂŠtodo `AdditionalBeanBuildItem.Builder#setDefaultScope()` . O escopo padrĂŁo sĂł ĂŠ utilizado caso nĂŁo haja nenhum escopo declarado na classe do bean."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If no default scope is specified the `@Dependent` pseudo-scope is used."
msgstr "Caso nĂŁo seja especificado nenhum escopo padrĂŁo, ĂŠ utilizado o pseudo-escopo `@Dependent` ."

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_Reason 2_: Class Is Discovered but Has No Bean Defining Annotation"
msgstr "_Motivo 2_ : A classe foi encontrada, mas nĂŁo possui nenhuma anotaĂ§ĂŁo que defina um bean"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In Quarkus, the application is represented by a single bean archive with the https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1.html#default_bean_discovery[bean discovery mode `annotated`, window=\"_blank\"].\n"
"Therefore, bean classes that don't have a https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1.html#bean_defining_annotations[bean defining annotation, window=\"_blank\"] are ignored.\n"
"Bean defining annotations are declared on the class-level and include scopes, stereotypes and `@Interceptor`."
msgstr "No Quarkus, a aplicaĂ§ĂŁo ĂŠ representada por um Ăşnico arquivo de beans com o link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1.html#default_bean_discovery[modo de descoberta de beans anotado] . Portanto, as classes de beans que nĂŁo possuem uma link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/cdi/4.1/jakarta-cdi-spec-4.1.html#bean_defining_annotations[anotaĂ§ĂŁo de definiĂ§ĂŁo de bean] sĂŁo ignoradas. As anotaĂ§Ăľes de definiĂ§ĂŁo de bean sĂŁo declaradas no nĂ­vel da classe e incluem escopos, estereĂłtipos e `@Interceptor` ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_Solution 1_: Use the `AutoAddScopeBuildItem`. This build item can be used to add a scope to a class that meets certain conditions."
msgstr "_SoluĂ§ĂŁo 1_ : Utilize o `AutoAddScopeBuildItem` . Esse item de compilaĂ§ĂŁo pode ser usado para adicionar um escopo a uma classe que atenda a determinadas condiĂ§Ăľes."

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`AutoAddScopeBuildItem` Example"
msgstr "Exemplo de `AutoAddScopeBuildItem`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Find all classes annotated with `@Scheduled`."
msgstr "Encontre todas as classes anotadas com `@Scheduled` ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Add `@Singleton` as default scope. Classes already annotated with a scope are skipped automatically."
msgstr "Adicione `@Singleton` como escopo padrĂŁo. As classes que jĂĄ estejam anotadas com um escopo sĂŁo ignoradas automaticamente."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_Solution 2_: If you need to process classes annotated with a specific annotation, then it's possible to extend the set of bean defining annotations via the `BeanDefiningAnnotationBuildItem`."
msgstr "_SoluĂ§ĂŁo 2_ : Caso precise processar classes anotadas com uma anotaĂ§ĂŁo especĂ­fica, ĂŠ possĂ­vel ampliar o conjunto de anotaĂ§Ăľes que definem beans por meio do `BeanDefiningAnnotationBuildItem` ."

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`BeanDefiningAnnotationBuildItem` Example"
msgstr "Exemplo de `BeanDefiningAnnotationBuildItem`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Add `org.eclipse.microprofile.graphql.GraphQLApi` to the set of bean defining annotations."
msgstr "Adicione `org.eclipse.microprofile.graphql.GraphQLApi` ao conjunto de anotaĂ§Ăľes que definem beans."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Bean classes added via `BeanDefiningAnnotationBuildItem` are _not removable_ by default, i.e. the resulting beans must not be removed even if they are considered unused.\n"
"However, you can change the default behaviour.\n"
"See also <<cdi-reference.adoc#remove_unused_beans,Removing Unused Beans>> and <<unremovable_builditem>> for more details."
msgstr "As classes de bean adicionadas por meio `do `BeanDefiningAnnotationBuildItem`` _nĂŁo_ sĂŁo _removĂ­veis_ por padrĂŁo; ou seja, os beans resultantes nĂŁo devem ser removidos, mesmo que sejam considerados nĂŁo utilizados. No entanto, ĂŠ possĂ­vel alterar o comportamento padrĂŁo. Consulte tambĂŠm xref:cdi-reference.adoc#remove_unused_beans[âRemovendo beans nĂŁo utilizados] â e â <<unremovable_builditem>> â para obter mais detalhes."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It is also possible to specify the default scope.\n"
"The default scope is only used if there is no scope declared on the bean class."
msgstr "TambĂŠm ĂŠ possĂ­vel especificar o escopo padrĂŁo. O escopo padrĂŁo sĂł ĂŠ utilizado caso nĂŁo haja nenhum escopo declarado na classe do bean."

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_Reason 3_: Class Was Discovered and Has a Bean Defining Annotation but Was Removed"
msgstr "_Motivo 3_ : A classe foi identificada e possui uma anotaĂ§ĂŁo de definiĂ§ĂŁo de bean, mas foi removida"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cdi-integration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The container attempts to <<cdi-reference.adoc#remove_unused_beans,remove all unused beans>> during the build by default.\n"
"This optimization allows for _framework-level dead code elimination_.\n"
"In a few special cases, it's not possible to correctly identify an unused bean.\n"
"In particular, Quarkus is not able to detect the usage of the `CDI.current()` static method yet.\n"
"Extensions can eliminate possible false positives by producing an `UnremovableBeanBuildItem`."
msgstr "Por padrĂŁo, o contĂŞiner tenta xref:cdi-reference.adoc#remove_unused_beans[remover todos os beans nĂŁo utilizados] durante a compilaĂ§ĂŁo. Essa otimizaĂ§ĂŁo permite _a eliminaĂ§ĂŁo de cĂłdigo morto no nĂ­vel da estrutura_ . Em alguns casos especĂ­ficos, nĂŁo ĂŠ possĂ­vel identificar corretamente um bean nĂŁo utilizado. Em particular, o Quarkus ainda nĂŁo ĂŠ capaz de detectar o uso do mĂŠtodo estĂĄtico ``CDI.current()` `. As extensĂľes podem eliminar possĂ­veis falsos positivos gerando um ``UnremovableBeanBuildItem` `."

